  "detailed_description": "<strong>Meet Hoverkitty!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/cef47902b514d8c5ea11f2ba8eceb954.avif?t=1728392860\" width=424 height=420 /></span><br><br><strong>Hoverkitty</strong> is one cute, lovable, courageous, and determined futuristic momma!<br><br><strong> ... EVERYTHING</strong> you've been trained to expect of a strong female lead in the 21st century!<br><br>Join <strong>Hoverkitty</strong> as she enters the <strong>HOVERVERSE</strong> to rescue her best friend <strong>Hoverflea</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/096c047494690aecadc6a2b7dbc2689c.avif?t=1728392860\" width=420 height=394 /></span><br><br>Defeat fiendish foes along the way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fiendish Foes:</h2><strong>Shadowcat</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/db4bbcbcaa63e7c16885e9e533565671.avif?t=1728392860\" width=510 height=458 /></span><br><br><strong>Boss Slave</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/67e4ea7ddd2588f0d006939f7d229df5.avif?t=1728392860\" width=504 height=718 /></span><br><br><strong>Boss</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/a9f118e155aa67402d16ceb7a4dc41d7.avif?t=1728392860\" width=502 height=552 /></span><br><br>Recruit misunderstood monsters along the way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Misunderstood Monsters:</h2><strong>Spiders</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/128c125508d0582a3d38447212a00b98.avif?t=1728392860\" width=514 height=288 /></span><br><br>... AND the MOST MISUNDERTSOOD MONSTER of ALL <strong>Mother</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/7b8274d50f071b008df81a1c3dc24eb9.avif?t=1728392860\" width=600 height=422 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter the Hoververse!</h2>A guided, at times puzzling, self-meditation in what it means to be Hoverkitty whilst on a journey through the hazardous <strong>Hoververse</strong> to rescue her friend <strong>Hoverflea</strong>!<br><br><br>Enjoy the hundreds of hours of effort by solo game developer Bridget as she releases her very first 3D, casual, adventure platformer!<br><br><strong>If you enjoy cats and a chiller kind of pace, then join us in the Hoververse!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Meet Hoverkitty!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/cef47902b514d8c5ea11f2ba8eceb954.avif?t=1728392860\" width=424 height=420 /></span><br><br><strong>Hoverkitty</strong> is one cute, lovable, courageous, and determined futuristic momma!<br><br><strong> ... EVERYTHING</strong> you've been trained to expect of a strong female lead in the 21st century!<br><br>Join <strong>Hoverkitty</strong> as she enters the <strong>HOVERVERSE</strong> to rescue her best friend <strong>Hoverflea</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/096c047494690aecadc6a2b7dbc2689c.avif?t=1728392860\" width=420 height=394 /></span><br><br>Defeat fiendish foes along the way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fiendish Foes:</h2><strong>Shadowcat</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/db4bbcbcaa63e7c16885e9e533565671.avif?t=1728392860\" width=510 height=458 /></span><br><br><strong>Boss Slave</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/67e4ea7ddd2588f0d006939f7d229df5.avif?t=1728392860\" width=504 height=718 /></span><br><br><strong>Boss</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/a9f118e155aa67402d16ceb7a4dc41d7.avif?t=1728392860\" width=502 height=552 /></span><br><br>Recruit misunderstood monsters along the way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Misunderstood Monsters:</h2><strong>Spiders</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/128c125508d0582a3d38447212a00b98.avif?t=1728392860\" width=514 height=288 /></span><br><br>... AND the MOST MISUNDERTSOOD MONSTER of ALL <strong>Mother</strong>:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928290/extras/7b8274d50f071b008df81a1c3dc24eb9.avif?t=1728392860\" width=600 height=422 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enter the Hoververse!</h2>A guided, at times puzzling, self-meditation in what it means to be Hoverkitty whilst on a journey through the hazardous <strong>Hoververse</strong> to rescue her friend <strong>Hoverflea</strong>!<br><br><br>Enjoy the hundreds of hours of effort by solo game developer Bridget as she releases her very first 3D, casual, adventure platformer!<br><br><strong>If you enjoy cats and a chiller kind of pace, then join us in the Hoververse!</strong>",
